hadiths[109]{hadithnumber,text}:
3446,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman shakhs ye gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur main Allah ka Rasool hun to uska khoon (yani qatl karna) faqat teen Suraton ki wajeh se halal hai, jaan ke badley jaan (qatil ko qatl karna) shaadi shuda zaani aur Deen se murtad ho kar jamaat chhodney wala.'' muttafaq aleh."
3447,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''momin apney Deen mein badhta rehta hai jab tak ke kisi haram khoon ka irtikab na karey.'' Bukhari."
3448,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat logon ke darmiyan sab se pehley khoonon ke barey mein faisla kiya jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
3449,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn agar mera kisi kafir shakhs se muqabla ho jaey aur ham dono eik doosrey par hamla aawar ho jaeyn aur wo talwaar ke zariey mujh par waar karey aur merey eik haath ko kaat daley , phir wo mujh se bachney ke liye eik darkht ke peechhey chup jaey aur kahe main Allah ke hukm ke samney sar taslim kham karta hun, aur eik riwayat mein hai : jab maine usey qatl karney ka irada kiya to usney kaha : ''(La Ilaah illallah) ''to kya uskey kalima padhney ke baad main usey qatl kar dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey qatl na karo.'' usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! usney mera eik haath kaat dala, (us ka kya baney ga?) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey qatl na karo agar tum ne usey qatl kiya to wo terey maqam aur martabe par aa jaeyga jo ke qatl karney se pehley tera tha, aur tum uskey maqam aur martabe par ho jaaogey jo kalima padhney se pehley uska tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
3450,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein juhaina qabiley ki taraf rawana farmaya, main unke eik aadmi ke muqabil aaya to maine is par neze ka waar karna chaha to usney kalima padh liya , lekin maine is par waar karkey usey qatl kar diya, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bataya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne usey qatl kar diya halanke usney gawahi de-di ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! usney to mehaz jaan bachaney ke liye kalima padha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kya uska dil cheer kar dekh liya tha?'' muttafaq aleh."
3451,Aur Jundub bin Abdullah Bajli (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab wo qiyamat ke roz (La Ilaah illallah) ke sath aaeyga to tum uska samna kis tarah karogey? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye baat kaee baar farmaee. rawahu Muslim.
3452,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi mua'ahid (jis ke saath muhaaida ho) (zimmi) ko qatl kiya to wo jannat ki khushbu bhi nahin paeyga halanke uski khushbu chaalis saal ki masafat (doori) se mehsus ki jaeygi.'' Bukhari."
3453,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne apney aap ko pahad se gira kar maar liya to wo jahannam mein girta rahega aur is mein hamesha hamesha rahega . aur jisney zahar ke zariey khudkushi ki to uska zahar uskey haath mein hoga jisey wo jahannam ki aag mein peeta rahega. aur is mein hamesha-hamesha rahega, aur jisney lohey (ke kisi aaley) ke zariey khudkushi ki to uska hathiyar uskey haath mein hoga aur wo jahannam ki aag mein usey apney pet mein ghonptaa rahega aur wo is mein hamesha-hamesha rahega.'' muttafaq aleh."
3454,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney apna gala ghoont kar khudkushi ki to wo jahannam mein bhi gala ghonteyga aur jo neza maar kar khudkushi kerega to wo jahannam mein bhi apney aap ko neza maarta rahega.'' Bukhari."
3455,"Hazrat Jundub bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se pehley logon main eik aadmi tha jo zakhmi ho gaya to usney be-sabri ka muzahira kiya, usney chhuri pakdi aur apna (zakhmi) haath kaat dala, uska khoon behta raha yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaya, Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''merey bandey ne khud ko qatl karney mein mujh se jaldi ki isliye maine is par jannat haram kar di.'' muttafaq aleh."
3456,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina ki taraf hijrat farmaee to Tufail bin Amr Dosi (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki taraf hijrat ki aur unke sath unki qom ke eik aadmi ne bhi hijrat ki, wo shakhs bimar ho gaya aur usney be-sabri ka muzahira kiya aur usney apni chhuri li aur us se apna haath kaat dala jis se khoon bahney laga yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaya. Tufail bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey khuwab mein dekha ke uski haiyat achchhi hai aur usney apney haath dhanp rakhey hain, unhoney us se puchha : terey rab ne terey sath kya maamla kiya? to usney kaha : usney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf meri hijrat ki wajeh se mujhey maaf farma diya, Tufail bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main aap ko haath dhaanpey huey kyon dekh raha hun? usney kaha : mujhey kaha gaya ke ham tumharey us hissey ko durust nahin karengey jisey tum ne khud kharab kiya hai, Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ye qissa arz kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! aur uskey dono haathon ko bhi maaf farma.'' rawahu Muslim."
3457,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih Ka'abi (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khuza'aa (qabiley walo) ! tum ne Huzail ke us maqtool ko qatl kiya, aur Allah ki qism ! main uski diyat ada kar deta hun, jisney uskey baad kisi ko qatl kiya to uskey warison ko do chizon ke darmiyan ikhtiyar hai, agar wo pasand karen to usey qatl karen aur agar chahen to diyat ley lein.'' isey Tirmizi aur Imam Shafai ne riwayat kiya hai aur Imam Baghwi ne Sharahus-sunnah main apni sanad se riwayat kiya hai aur unhoney sarahat ki ke Abu-Shuraih ki sanad se ye hadees sahee-hain mein nahin hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Shafai."
3458,Aur unhon (Baghwi (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : un dono (Imam Bukhari aur Imam Muslim) ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se usi mafhoom ki riwayat naqal ki hai. muttafaq aleh.
3459,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi ne eik londi ka sar do patharon ke darmiyan kuchal diya, us se puchha gaya, tumharey sath ye sulook kis ne kiya? kya falan ne? kya falan ne? yahan tak ke us Yahudi ka naam liya gaya to usney sar ke isharay se kaha : haan, us Yahudi ko pesh kiya gaya to usney aetraaf kar liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to uskey sar ko pathar ke sath kuchal diya gaya. muttafaq aleh."
3460,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, unki phuphi Rubaie (Raziallahu anhu) ne ansaar ki eik londi ke samney ke daant tod diye to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qisaas ka hukm farmaya to Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke phoophaa Anas bin Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ki qism ! Allah ke Rasool ! uskey daant nahin todey jaeyngey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Anas ! Allah ki kitab mein qisaas ka hukm hai.'' wo log diyat leney par razi ho gaey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke kuch bandey aisey bhi hain ke agar wo Allah par qism utha len to Allah unki qism ko sachcha kar deta hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3461,"Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se daryaft kiya, kya tumharey paas koi aisi chiz hai jo Quran mein na ho? unhoney farmaya is zaat ki qism ! jisney daney ko phada aur rooh ko paida farmaya ! hamarey paas sirf wohi kuchh hai jo Quran mein hai, albatta Deen ka wo Faham hai jo bandey ko Allah ki kitab se ata kiya jata hai aur jo kuchh saheefe mein likha hua hai (wo hamarey paas hai). maine arz kiya : saheefe mein kya hai? unhoney farmaya : ''diyat, qaidi chhudaney aur ye ke kisi musalman ko kafir ke badle mein qatl na kiya jaey, ke mutalliq ehkamaat. Bukhari. aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ke ''kisi jaan ko nahaq qatl na kiya jaey.'' kitabul-ilm mein zikr ki gaee hai."
3462,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ke yahan puri duniya ka tabah aur barbad ho jana eik musalman aadmi ke qatl ke muqabley mein ziyada aasan hai.'' Tirmizi, Nasai . aur baaz ne isey moquf qarar diya hai aur yehi ziyada sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
3463,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne usey Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja.
3464,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar zamin aur aasman ke tamam baasi eik momin ke qatl karney mein shareek paey jaeyn to Allah un sab ko chehrey ke bal jahannam mein phenk dega.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3465,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat maqtool qatil ko lekar aaeyga us (qatil) ki peshani aur uska sar maqtool ke haath mein hoga aur uski ragon se khoon beh raha hoga. aur wo kahega : rab ji ! isney mujhey kyon qatl kiya? yahan tak ke wo usey arsh ke qarib ley jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
3466,"Hazrat Abu-Umama bin Sehal bin Hanif se riwayat hai ke Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne ''yoamuddar'' (jin dino baaghiyon ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghair kar rakha tha) logon ko dekh kar farmaya ke main tumhen Allah ki qism de-kar poochhta hun : kya tum Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke us farman se aagah nahin ho? ke ''kisi musalman shakhs ka khoon teen mein se kisi eik wajeh par durust hai : shaadi shuda honey ke baad zina karna ya Islam ke baad kufr karna ya kisi jaan ko nahaq qatl karna, aur wo uskey baais qatl kiya jaeyga.'' Allah ki qism ! maine na to daure jahiliyat mein zina kiya aur na zamanae-Islam mein, maine jab se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki us waqt se aaj tak kabhi murtad nahin hua , aur maine kisi aisi jaan ko qatl nahin kiya jisey Allah ne haram qarar diya hai, to phir tum mujhey kyon qatl kartey ho? Tirmizi, Nasai , ibne-Maja. aur Darmi mein sirf hadees ke alfaz hain. rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3467,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak momin kisi ka nahaq khoon nahin karta to wo itaat guzari aur naik kaamon ki baja aawri mein muste'ad rehta hai aur jab wo kisi ka nahaq khoon kar leta hai to wo susti aur thakawat ka shikar ho jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3468,"Hazrat Abu-Darda , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''umeed hai ke Allah her gunah maaf farma dey alawa us shakhs ke jo haalate-shirk mein faut ho, aur jisney amadan kisi momin ko qatl kiya ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3469,Hazrat Imam Nasai ne usey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Nasai.
3470,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''masaajid mein hudood qaaim na ki jaeyn aur na aulad ka walid se qisaas liya jaey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi ."
3471,"Hazrat Abu-Rimsa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main apney walid ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey sath ye kon hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : mera beta hai. aap iskey mutalliq gawah rahiye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aagah raho ! na to terey gunah ka us se muwaakhiza (sawal) hoga na uskey gunah ka tujh se muwaakhiza (sawal) hoga.'' aur Sharahus-sunnah mein is hadees ke shuru mein mazeed alfaz hain : unhoney bayan kiya : main apney walid ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to merey walid ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki pusht par jo chiz (mohare nabuwat) thi wo dekh li to arz kiya mujhey ijazat den , main is chiz ka ilaj karta hun jo aap ki pusht par hai kyonkey main tabeeb hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum rafeeq ho aur Allah tabeeb hai.'' (rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3472,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Suraqa bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhoney kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baap ko uskey bete se qisaas dilwaya aur bete ka baap se qisaas nahin dilwaya . Tirmizi, aur unhoney isey zaeef qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3473,"Hazrat Hasan Basri (Raziallahu anhu), Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo apney ghulam ko qatl kerega, ham usey qatl karengey aur jo apney ghulam ke aaza (naak waghera) kaateyga ham uskey aaza kaatein gey.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja , Darmi. aur Imam Nasai ne eik dusri riwayat mein izafa naqal kiya hai : ''jo apney ghulam ko khassi kerega ham usey khassi karengey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja, Darmi aur Nasai."
3474,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney baap se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne amadan (jan-bujhkar) qatl kiya to usey maqtool ke warison ke hawaley kiya jaeyga, agar wo chahen to (usey) qatl kar den aur agar wo chahen to diyat ley lein. aur wo tees hiqqa (oontni ka wo bacha jo teen saal mukammal karney ke baad umr ke chauthey saal mein dakhil ho) tees jazaa (wo oontni jo paanchwen saal mein dakhil ho) aur chaalis hamila oontniyaan hai. aur wo jis chiz par musaalihat kar lein to wo unke liye hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3475,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalmanon ke khoon (qisaas aur diyat mein) masaawi (barabar) hain, aur unke aam aadmi ki amaan ka bhi lihaz rakha jaeyga aur un se door-daraaz wala shakhs maale ghanimat unke nazdik waley par lotayega aur wo dushman ke muqabley mein baham (aapas mein) dast wahid ki tarah hain, sun lo ! kisi musalman ko kisi kafir ke badley mein qatl nahin kiya jaeyga aur na kisi muaahida (zimmi) ko uskey ehad mein qatl kiya jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3476,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne usey ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja.
3477,"Hazrat Abu-Shuraih Khuzaae (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ka koi aziz qatl ho jaey ya koi zakhmi kar diya jaey to usey teen mein se eik ka ikhtiyar hai, agar wo chauthi chiz ka irada kar ley to uskey haath pakad lo, wo qisaas le-ley, ya maaf kar dey ya diyat le-ley. agar usney is mein se koi chiz ley li aur phir uskey baad ziyadti ki to uskey liye jahannam ki aag hai jis mein wo hamesha hamesha rahega.'' rawahu Darmi."
3478,"Hazrat Taaus, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs balwe mein maara jaey, maslan ladney waley eik doosrey par pathar phenk rahey they ya kodey maar rahey they ya lathiyan barsa rahey they to wo qatl khataa hai aur uski diyat, diyate-khataa ki jaisi hogi . aur jisney iradatan qatl kiya to wo (qatil) qabile-qisaas hai, aur jo shakhs us (qisaas) ke darmiyan haael(rukawet) ho jaey, is par Allah ki lanat aur uska ghazab hai, us se na to nafl qubul hoga aur na farz.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3479,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main, diyat leney ke baad qatl karney waley ko maaf nahin karunga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3480,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ke jism mein koi zakhm lag jaey aur wo maaf kar dey to uski wajeh se Allah uska eik darja buland kar deta hai aur uski eik khata maaf farma deta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3481,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik aadmi ke qatl ke badley mein paanch ya saat aadmiyon ko qatl kiya unhoney usey dhokey se qatl kiya tha, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar uskey qatl par san'aa ke tamam log jamaa hotey to main (uskey badley mein) sab ko qatl kar deta.'' rawahu Maalik."
3482,Hazrat Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne usi ki jaisi ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. Bukhari.
3483,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, falan shakhs ne mujhey hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat maqtool apney qatil ko lekar aaeyga aur wo kahega : (rab ji !) is se poochen ke usney mujhey qatl kyon kiya? to wo kahega : maine isey falan ki saltanat / falan ki nusrat par qatl kiya.'' Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : zalim ki iaa'nat (madad) se bacho. rawahu Nasai."
3484,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi momin ke qatl par thodi si baat ke barabar bhi madad ki to wo Allah se us haal mein mulaqat kerega ke uski dono aakhon ke beech likha hoga : ''Allah ki rehmat se na-umeed.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3485,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi kisi aadmi ko pakad kar rakhey aur doosra aadmi usey qatl kar dey to qatil ko qatl kiya jaeyga aur pakadney waley ko qaid kiya jaeyga.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni."
3486,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye aur ye yani chhanguli aur angoothaa (diyat mein) barabar hain.'' Bukhari."
3487,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano lahyaan ki eik aurat ke hamal ke murda haalat mein khatam ho janey par eik ghulam ya londi ka faisla kiya tha, phir wo aurat jiskey mutalliq aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghulam ka faisla kiya tha wo faut ho gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla diya ke uski meeras uskey beton aur uskey shohar ke liye hai jabkey uski diyat uskey usba (rishte daaron) par hai. muttafaq aleh."
3488,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, huzail qabiley ki do aurten lad padin to un mein se eik ne dusri par pathar maara aur usey aur uskey janeen (pet ke bachchey) ko qatl kar diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla diya ke uskey janeen ki diyat eik ghulam ya eik londi hai aur aurat ki diyat uskey khandan (aurat ke baap ki taraf se rishte-daar (usba)) par hai. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski aulad aur jo unke sath hain unko uska waris banaya. muttafaq aleh."
3489,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aurten sautan thin, un mein se eik ne dusri ko pathar ya khemey ka baans maara to uska janeen (pet ka bachcha) gir gaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne janeen ke barey mein ghulam ya londi ka faisla diya aur usey us aurat ke usba par muqarrar farmaya. ye Tirmizi ki riwayat hai, aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : aurat ne apni sautan ko jo ke hamila thi, khemey ka baans maara to usney usey qatl kar diya, aur kaha : un mein se eik lihyaaniya thi, raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqtoola ki diyat qaatila ke usba (rishte daaron) par muqarrar farmaee aur jo us (maqtoola) ke pet mein tha uski diyat eik ghulam muqarrar ki. rawahu Tirmizi aur Muslim."
3490,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! khataa ki diyat, shubha-amad ki diyat ke jaisi hai, jo kodey aur lathi se ho, uski (diyat) sau oont hai, jin mein se chaalis hamila hongi.'' rawahu Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3491,"Aur Abu-Dawood ne un (Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, aur Sharahus-sunnah mein Masaabeh ke alfaz sirf ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hain. (rawahu Abu-Dawood aur al-Baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3492,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Muhammad bin Amr bin Hazam apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale Yamen ke naam khat likha aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khat mein tha : ''jisney kisi musalman ko amadan nahaq qatl kiya to uska qisaas uskey haath ke amal ki wajeh se hai, magar ye ke maqtool ke waaris razi ho jaeyn.'' aur us (khat) mein ye bhi tha : ''aadmi ko aurat ke badley mein qatl kiya jaeyga.'' aur is mein tha : ''kisi jaan ki diyat so oont hai. aur soney walon par eik hazar deenar, aur naak ki diyat jab usey mukammal taur par kaat diya jaey, so oont hai. daanton ke barey mein diyat hai, honton ke barey mein diyat hai, foton ke barey mein diyat hai, sharm-gah ke barey mein diyat hai. kamar ke barey mein diyat hai. aakhon ke barey mein diyat hai. eik paaon ki nisf (aadhi) diyat hai, dimagh ki jhilli tak pahunchney waley zakhm par eik tihai diyat hai. pet ke andar pahunchney waley zakhm main eik tihai diyat hai. haddi ko jagah se hata deney waley zakhm mein pandarah oont diyat hai. haath aur paaon ki her ungli mein das oont diyat hai. aur daant ki diyat paanch oont hai.'' Nasai , Darmi. aur Imam Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''aankh mein pachas , haath mein pachas , paaon mein pachas aur haddi zahir karney waley zakhm par paanch oont diyat hai.'' rawahu Nasai, Darmi aur Maalik."
3493,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haddi zahir karney waley zakhm mein aur her daant mein paanch paanch oont diyat muqarrar ki hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Nasai , Darmi , jabkey Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja ne pehla jumla naqal kiya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai, Darmi, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3494,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haathon aur paaon ki ungliyon ko barabar qarar diya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi."
3495,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(diyat ke barey mein) tamam ungliyan barabar hain, tamam daant barabar hain, samney waley daant aur daadhein barabar hain, ye aur ye (chhanguli aur angoothaa) barabar hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3496,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke saal khutba irshad farmaya to farmaya : '' logo ! Islam mein koi naya muahida nahin, aur daure-jahiliyat mein jo muahida tha Islam is mein izafa nahin karta albatta usey mazbut karta hai, momin dushman ke muqabley mein baham (aapas mein) dast wahid ki tarah hain eik adnaa musalman bhi kisi kafir ko panah dey sakta hai aur un mein se jo door-daraaz hai wo bhi un tak pahunchata hai, aur unke lashkar jihad mein shareek na honey walon ko bhi maale-ghanimat mein shareek kartey hain. kisi momin ko kafir ke badley mein qatl nahin kiya jaeyga, kafir ki diyat, musalman ki diyat se aadhi hai, Zakat wasul karney wala na apney paas Zakat mangaye aur na Zakat deney waley apna maal door ley jaeyn aur unke sadqaat unke gharon hi se wasul kiye jaeyn.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''zimmi ki diyat, azaad aadmi ki diyat ke aadhi hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
3497,"Hazrat Khashaf bin Malik, ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khataa ki diyat bees ''binte-makhaz'' , bees ''ibne makhaz nar '', bees ''binte-labun '', bees ''jazaa'' aur bees ''hiqa'' muqarrar farmaee. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai . rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai. aur sahih ye hai ke ye ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) par moquf hai. jabkey Khashaf majhool hai. us se sirf yehi eik riwayat marwi (bayan) hai. aur Sharahus-sunnah mein riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke eik maqtool ki sadqe ke oonton mein se so oont diyat ada ki, aur sadqe ke oonton mein ''ibne makhaz'' nahin tha. in mein sirf ''ibne-labun'' they."
3498,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein diyat ki qeemat aath sau Dinar thi ya aath hazar dirham thi, aur un dino ehle-kitab ki diyat musalmanon ki diyat se nisf (aadhi) thi unhoney mazeed farmaya : diyat ka maamla isi tarah tha yahan tak ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa baney to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba irshad farmaya ke oont mahnge ho gaey hain, raawi bayan kartey hain ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne soney walon par hazar Dinar , chaandi walon par baara hazar dirham , gaaey walon par do sau gayen , bakriyon walon par do hazar bakriyan , jodey (soot) walon par do-sau jodey muqarrar farmaai , raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne zimmiyon ki diyat chhod di, aur jab unhoney diyat badhaai to usey na badhaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3499,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne diyat baara hazar (dirham) muqarrar farmaee. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi."
3500,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dehatiyon par diyat khataa chaar-sau Dinar ya uskey masaawi chaandi muqarrar farmaya kartey they. aur is mein oonton ki qeemat ka lihaz rakhtey they. jab (oonton ki) qeemat badh jati to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us (diyat) ki qeemat badha detey they, aur jab unki qeemat kam ho jati to aap us diyat ki qeemat kam kar detey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein diyat ki qeemat chaar so Dinar se aath so Dinar tak pahunch gaee thi. aur chaandi se uskey masaawi aath hazar dirham tak pahunch gaee thi, raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gaaey walon par do-sau gaayen aur bakriyon walon par do-hazar bakriyan diyat muqarrar farmaee. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak diyat maqtool ke waarison ke darmiyan meeras hai.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla farmaya ke aurat ki diyat uskey usba (rishte daaron) par hai, aur qatil kisi chiz ka waris nahin baneyga. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3501,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shubha-amad (jis par jaan-bujhkar qatl karne ka shubah ho) ki diyat, diyate-amad ki tarah mughalliza (sakht) hai aur us (shubha amad) ke mujrim ko qatl nahin kiya jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3502,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni jagah par Sabit reh janey wali aankh ki eik tihai diyat muqarrar farmaee. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3503,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Amr ne Abu-Salma aur unhoney Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne janeen (pet ke bachchey) ke barey mein ghulam ya londi ya ghoda ya khachchar bator diyat muqarrar farmaya. Abu-Dawood ne isey riwayat kiya aur farmaya : Hammad bin Salma aur Khalid Waasti ne ye hadees Muhammad bin Amr se riwayat ki aur unhoney ghodey ya khachchar ka zikr nahin kiya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3504,Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur unhoney apney dada se riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ilaj muaalija karey jabkey wo tibb mein mahir na ho to wo (mareez ki maut waqey honey par diyat ka ( zaamin hoga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai.
3505,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke gharib logon ke ghulam ne ameer logon ke ghulam ka kaan kaat diya to us (kaan kaatney waley ghulam) ke ghar waley, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhoney arz kiya, ham faqir log hain, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un par (diyat mein sey) kuchh bhi muqarrar na farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3506,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ''shubha-amad (jis par jaan-bujhkar qatl karne ka shubah ho) ki diyat teen qisam (ke oonton) par mushtamil hai : tentis hiqqa (teen saal mukammal karney ke baad chauthey saal mein dakhil oont) tentis jazaa (paanchwen saal mein dakhil) chauntees (chatey saal mein dakhil honey wali oontniyaan) aur wo sab hamila hon.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai farmaya : ''qatl khataa ki diyat chaar qisam ki oontniyaan hain : pachchis hiqqa , pachchis jazaa, pachchis banate laboon aur pachchis banate makhaz.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3507,"Hazrat Mujahid bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne shubha amad (jis par jaan-bujhkar qatl karne ka shubah ho) mein tees hiqa , tees jazaa aur chaalis hamila oontniyon ka faisla kiya jo ke chhe-saal se nau-saal ki umr ke darmiyan hon aur wo tamam hamila hon. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3508,"Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne janeen (pet ke bachchey) ke barey mein jisey uski maa ke pet mein qatl kiya jaey, eik ghulam ya eik londi ki diyat ka faisla kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jiskey khilaf faisla kiya tha usney kaha : main uski diyat kaisey ada karun jisney na-piya, na-khaya aur us se kalam kiya na koi cheekh maari. aur is tarah wo us qatl ko rayegaan qarar deta tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to kaahinon ka sathi hai.'' Maalik. Nasai ne isey mursal riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Maalik aur Nasai."
3509,Hazrat Abu-Dawood ne Saeed bin Musaiyeb an Abi Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se mausoolan riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3510,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar chopaey kisi ko zakhmi kar den to is par koi khoon-baha nahin, agar koi kaan mein dab kar mar jaey is par koi khoon-baha nahin aur jo shakhs kunwen mein gir kar mar jaey to uska khoon-baha nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
3511,"Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine ghazwae-tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shirkat ki, mera eik naukar tha uska kisi shakhs se jhagda ho gaya to un dono mein se kisi eik ne doosrey ka haath (daanton sey) chabaa dala to jis ka haath tha usney apney haath ko uskey munh se khincha to uskey samney ke daant gira diye, wo (shikaayat lekar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey daanton ko rayegaan (bekar) qarar diya aur uska badla na dilaaya aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wo apna haath tumharey munh mein rehney deta taake tum oont ki tarah usey chabaa daltey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3512,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ko apney maal ki hifazat kartey huey qatl kar diya jaey to wo Shahid hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3513,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi aaya to usney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn agar koi aadmi (nahaq taur par) mera maal leney ke iraday se aaye (to main kya karun?) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apna maal usey mat leney do.'' usney arz kiya, mujhey bataeyn agar wo mujh se jhagda karey to? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum bhi us se jhagda karo.'' usney arz kiya : mujhey bataeyn agar wo mujhey qatl kar dey? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Shahid ho.'' usney arz kiya : mujhey bataeyn agar main usey qatl kar dun? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jahannami hai.'' (tum par koi muwaakhiza (pakad) nahin) . rawahu Muslim."
3514,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''agar koi shakhs bila ijazat tumharey ghar mein jhaankey aur tum usey kankari maaro jis se uski aankh phoot jaey to tum par koi gunah nahin.'' muttafaq aleh.
3515,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darwazey ke surakh mein se jhaankaa , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas lakdi ya lohey ki kanghi numaa koi chiz thi jis se aap apna sar khujlaatey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mujhey pata hota ke tum mujhey dekh rahey ho to main usey tumhari dono aakhon mein chubho deta, dekhney hi ki wajeh se to ijazat lena muqarrar kiya gaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3516,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik aadmi ko kankariyaan phainktey huey dekha to unhoney kaha : kankariyaan mat phenko kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kankariyaan phainkney se mana farmaya hai aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us se na to shikar kiya ja sakta hai aur na dushman ko zakhmi kiya ja sakta hai lekin ye (phenkna) daant tod sakta hai aur aankh phod sakta hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
3517,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs hamari masjid aur hamarey baazar mein se guzrey aur uskey paas teer ho to wo uskey paikaan (nok) par haath rakhey taake us se koi musalman zakhmi na ho jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3518,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi aslaha ke zariey apney bhai ki taraf ishara na karey kyonkey wo nahin janta ke ho sakta hai shetan uskey haath se jhapat kar (uskey bhai par waar karey) isi tarah ye jahannam mein ja girey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3519,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs neze se apney bhai ki taraf ishara karey, farishtey is par lanat bhejtey rehtey hain, yahan tak ke wo usey rakh dey. chahey wo uska haqeeqi bhai hi kyon na ho.'' Bukhari."
3520,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs hamarey khilaf aslaha uthaey to wo ham mein se nahin.'' aur Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''jisney hamen dhoka diya wo ham mein se nahin.'' muttafaq aleh."
3521,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney hamarey khilaf talwaar uthai wo ham mein se nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
3522,"Hazrat Hisham bin Urwa apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Hisham bin Haakim Sham mein qome-anbaat ke kuchh logon ke paas se guzrey jinhen dhoop mein khada kiya gaya tha aur unke saron par zaitun ka tel dala ja raha tha, unhoney puchha : ye kya maamla hai? bataya gaya ke unhen tax ki adaegi na karne ki wajeh se saza di ja rahi hai, Hisham ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''wo be-shak Allah un logon ko azab dega jo logon ko duniya mein (nahaq) azab aur saza detey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
3523,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tumhari umr daraz hui to qarib hai ke tum kuchh aisey log dekhogey jinkey haathon mein gaaey ki dam jaisey (kodey) hongey, wo subah aur Sham (hamesha) Allah ke ghazab aur narazi mein rahengey.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' wo Allah ki lanat mein Sham kartey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
3524,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannamiyon ke do giroh aisey hain, jinhen maine nahin dekha, eik wo log jinkey paas gaaey ki dumon jaisey kodey hongey jinkey sath wo logon ko maartay hongey, aur wo aurten jo libas pehan kar bhi uriyaan (nangi) hongi, maael karney wali , matak matak kar chalney wali hongi , unke sar bakhti oonton ki jhuki hui kohaanon ki tarah uthey huey hongey, ye dono giroh na to jannat mein jaeyngey aur na uski khushbu paeyngey, halanke uski khushbu door-daraaz tak pheli hogi.'' rawahu Muslim."
3525,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi (kisi ko) maarey to wo chehrey se ijtinab karey, kyonkey Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko apni surat par paida farmaya hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3526,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney parda uthaya aur bila ijazat ghar mein nazar dali aur ghar walon ki parde ki chiz ko dekh liya to usney eik qabile sazaa jurm kiya jis ka karna uskey liye halal nahin tha, aur agar us waqt, jab usney nazar dali , eik aadmi uskey samney aa gaya aur usney uski aankh phod di, main uski sarzanish nahin karunga, aur agar aadmi kisi aisey darwazey se guzrey jis ka koi parda na ho aur na wo band ho aur wo dekh ley to uski koi ghalati nahin, ghalati to ghar walon ki hai.'' is hadees ko Tirmizi ne riwayat kiya hai, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3527,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne be niyaam talwaar kisi ko deney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood ."
3528,Hazrat Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ungliyon ke darmiyan tasma cheerney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3529,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney Deen ki hifazat kartey huey maara jaey to wo Shahid hai, jo shakhs apni jaan ki hifazat kartey huey maara jaey wo bhi Shahid hai, jo shakhs apney maal ki hifazat karta maara jaey wo bhi Shahid hai aur jo shakhs apney ehale w ayaal ki hifazat kartey maara jaey wo bhi Shahid hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ."
3530,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahannam ke saat darwazey hain un mein se eik darwaza us shakhs ke liye hai jisney meri ummat ke khilaf talwaar uthai, ya farmaya : ''(jisney) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat ke khilaf (talwaar uthai).'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi. aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''chopaey ke paaon se lagney wala zakhm rayegaan hai.'' (baabul-ghazab) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
3531,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij aur Sehal bin Abi Hashma se riwayat hai un dono ne bayan kiya ke Abdullah bin Sehal aur Mahisa bin Masood khaibar aaye aur wo dono khajuron ke jhund mein alag ho gaey, chunanche Abdullah bin Sehal qatl kar diye gaey. uskey baad Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal aur Masood ke dono bete Huwesa aur Mahisa Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur wo apney sathi ke mamley ke mutalliq baat karney lagey to Abdur Rehman ne , jo ke logon mein sab se chhotey they, baat karna shuru ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''badey ko uskey badey honey ka haq do.'' Yahya bin Saeed ne farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki murad thi ke jo sab se bada hai wo kalam karey. unhoney baat ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney maqtool sathi ki diyat ke mutalliq pachas qasmen utha kar haq daar bin saktey ho.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo aisa maamla hai ke ham ne usey dekha nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahood ke pachas aadmi qism utha kar tum se bari ho jaeyngey.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo to kafir log hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni taraf se unhen diyat ada farmaee, aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''tum pachas qasmen uthaoo aur apney qatil ya apney sathi ke mustahiq bin jaao.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni taraf se so oontniyaan bator diyat ada farmaaen. muttafaq aleh."
3532,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij bayan kartey hain, ansaar ka eik aadmi khaibar mein qatl ho gaya to uskey waaris Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhoney uskey mutalliq aap se zikr kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas do gawah hain jo tumharey sathi ke qatil par gawahi den?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wahan to koi musalman nahin tha aur wo to yahood hain aur wo is se badi chiz ke karne ki jurrat kar jatey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un mein se pachas aadmi chun lo aur un se half ley lo.'' unhoney inkar kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni taraf se uska fidya ada farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3533,"Hazrat Ikrima bayan kartey hain, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas kuchh zindeeq (ag ki puja karne waale) laye gaey to unhoney unhen zinda jala diya, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko is baat ka pata chala to unhoney farmaya : agar main hota to main unhen kabhi zinda na jalata kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se iski mumaaniat mojud hai (ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya) : ''Allah ke azab ke sath azab na do.'' ki wajeh se main unhen na jalata aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman : ''jo shakhs apna Deen (Islam) badal ley to usey qatl kar do.'' ke mutabiq main unhen qatl kar deta. Bukhari."
3534,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aag ka azab sirf Allah hi dega.'' Bukhari."
3535,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''an-qareeb aakhiri zamaney main eik qom ka zuhoor hoga jo nau-umar magar aqal se zaeef hongey, wo ba-zahir nihayat ma'qool kaam karengey, lekin unka eman unke halaq se tajawuz nahin kerega, wo Deen se is tarah nikal jaeyngey jaisey teer shikar se nikal jata hai, tum unhen jahan paao wahin qatl kar do kyonkey unhen qatl karney mein roze-qiyamat unke qatil ke liye ajr hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3536,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat do girohon mein munqasim ho (bat) jaeygi aur in dono ke beech se eik khaariji jamaat roonumaa hogi , unka khatima wo log karengey jo haq ke ziyada qarib hongey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3537,"Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hajjatul-wadaa ke moqe par farmaya : ''merey baad eik doosrey ki gardanen kaat kar kafir na bin jana.'' muttafaq aleh."
3538,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab do musalman milen aur un mein se eik apney bhai par aslaha taan ley to wo dono jahannam ke kinarey par hotey hain, jab un mein se koi apney muqabil ko qatl kar deta hai to wo dono ikhattey jahannam mein dakhil ho jatey hain.'' aur un se eik dusri riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab do musalman apni talwaarein soont kar samney aa jatey hain to qatil aur maqtool jahannami hain.'' maine arz kya : qatil to hai lekin maqtool kis wajeh se? (ke wo mazloom honey ke bawajud jahannami hai) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kyonkey wo apney sathi ( mud muqabil ( ko qatl karney par utaru tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
3539,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ukul ke kuch log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unhoney Islam qubul kar liya. Madina ki aab w hua unhen muwaafiq na aai to aapney unhen sadqa ke oonton ke paas janey ka hukm farmaya taake wahan wo unka doodh aur peshab paiyein , unhoney aisey kya aur wo sehat yaab ho gaey, uskey baad wo murtad ho gaey aur unke charwaahon ko qatl karkey oont haank kar ley gaey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke taaqqub mein aadmi bhejey to wo unhen pakad kar ley aaye , aapney unke haath aur paaon kaat diye aur unki aakhon mein salaiyan pher di gaeen, phir unka khoon behta raha yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaey. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' unhoney unki aakhon mein salaiyan pher din .'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : '' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne salaiyon ke mutalliq hukm farmaya to unhen garm kya gaya aur unhen unki aakhon mein pher kar unhen dhoop mein phenk diya gaya wo pani talab kartey rahey magar unhen pani na diya gaya yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaey . muttafaq aleh."
3540,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen sadqa deney par aamada kya kartey they aur musla karney se mana farmaya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3541,Hazrat Imam Nasai ne usey Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai .
3542,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah apney baap se riwayat kartey hain, ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, aap qazaey-hajat ke liye tashrif ley gaey to ham ne eik chidiya ( surkh rang ki chidiya) dekhi, uskey sath uskey do bachey they, ham ne uskey bachey pakad liye to wo phad phadaney lagi, itney mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kis shakhs ne usey, uskey bachon ki wajeh se be qarar kar diya? uskey bachey usey wapis karo.'' aur aapney chewntiyon ka eik maskan dekha jisey ham ne jala diya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kis ne jalaaya hai? '' ham ne arz kya : ham ne, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aag ka azab dena sirf aag ke rab ke laaiq hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3543,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) aur Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein an-qareeb ikhtilaf w iftiraaq hoga. eik giroh baaten achi achi lekin kaam burey kerega. wo Quran padhengey lekin wo unke halaq se nichey nahin utrega. wo Deen se is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer shikar se nikal ( kar paar ho ( jata hai. wo Deen ki taraf nahin paltein gey yahan tak ke teer apney so faar (chutki jahan kamaan ka taant tikta hai) par wapis aa jaey. wo tamam makhluq se badtar hain. us shakhs ke liye khushkhabri hai jo unko qatl karta hai aur jisey wo qatl kar den, wo (b-zahir) Allah ki kitab ki taraf dawat dengey. lekin wo kisi chiz mein bhi ham mein se nahin hongey, jisney un se qitaal kya wo un (baqi ummatiyon) se Allah ke ziyada qarib hai.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : Allah ke Rasool! unki alamat kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sar mundaana.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3544,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo musalman ye gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, usey sirf teen wajhein mein se kisi eik wajeh se qatl karna jayez hai : shaadi ke baad zina waley ko rajm (sangsar) kya jaeyga, aur jo shakhs Allah aur uskey Rasool ke khilaf jang karey (yani daaku) ho, usey qatl kya jaeyga ya sooli par chadhaya jaeyga ya jala watan kya jaeyga. ya koi shakhs kisi jaan ko qatl kar dey to uskey badley mein usey qatl kya jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3545,"Hazrat ibne-abi Leila bayan kartey hain, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne hamen hadees bayan ki ke wo raat ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar kar rahey they, un mein se eik aadmi so gaya to kisi shakhs ne apni rassi li aur uski taraf gaya aur usey rassi ke sath baandh diya to wo (soney wala shakhs) ghabra gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi musalman ke liye ye laaiq nahin ke wo kisi musalman ko khof-zada karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3546,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu), Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne khiraaj wali zamin kharid li to usney apni hijrat (izzat) khatam kar li aur jisney kisi kafir ki gardan se zillat utaar kar apni gardan mein dal li to usney Islam ko peeth peechey dal diya .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3547,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (Yamen ke qabiley) khasam ki taraf eik lashkar rawana kya to un mein se kuch log bachney ke liye Namaz padhney lagey, lekin unhen tezi se qatl kya gaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uski khabar pahunchi to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke liye nisf diyat ka hukm farmaya, aur farmaya : ''main mushrikon ke darmiyan rehney waley tamam musalmanon (ke khoon ( se bariuzzimma hun.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! kis liye? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (wo kafiron se is qadr door rahen ke) unki aag nazar na aaye .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3548,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''emaan achcha qatl karney se mana karta hai. momin achcha (muttla kiye baghair) qatl nahin karta .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3549,"Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ghulam mushrekin ke ilaqey ki taraf farar ho jaey to uska khoon halal ho jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3550,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke eik Yahudi aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bura-bhala kaha karti thi aur aap ki mazammat kya karti thi, eik aadmi ne uska gala daba diya chunanche wo mar gaee to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska khoon rayegaan qarar de-diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3551,"Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jadugar ki had (yani saza) talwaar ke sath qatl karna hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
3552,"Hazrat Usama bin shareek (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs (Imam ke khilaf ( khurooj karey aur meri ummat ke darmiyan tafriq daley to uski gardan uda do.'' rawahu Nasai."
3553,"Hazrat shareek bin Shahab bayan kartey hain, meri tamanna thi ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi sahabi se miloon aur un se khawarij ke mutalliq daryaft karun, mein eid ke roz abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) se unke sathiyon ki mojudgi mein mila to maine un se kaha : kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khawaarij ka zikr kartey huey suna hai? unhoney arz kya : haan, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farmoodat ko apney kanon se suna hai aur aap ko apni aakhon se dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein kuch maal pesh kya gaya to aapney usey taqseem farmaya aur apney daain baaeyn walon ko ata kya, lekin aapney apni pichli janib walon ko kuch na diya to aap ki pichli janib se eik aadmi khada hua aur usney kaha : Muhammad! (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aapney taqseem mein insaf nahin kya, wo mundey huey baalon wala siyah faam shakhs tha, is par do safed kapdey they, (us par) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sakht naraz huey aur farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! merey baad tum koi aisa aadmi nahin paaogey jo mujh se ziyada adl karney wala ho.'' phir farmaya : '' aakhiri zamaney main eik qom ka zuhoor hoga, goya ye unhi mein se hai, wo Quran padhtey hongey magar wo unke halaq se nichey nahin utrega, wo Islam se is tarah nikal jaeyngey jis tarah teer shikar se nikal ( kar paar ho ( jata hai. sar mundaana unki alamat hogi , wo musalsal zahir hotey rahengey yahan tak ke unka aakhiri fard Masih dajjaal ke sath zahir hoga. jab tum un se milo to ( jaan lo ke) wo tamam makhluq se bad-tareen hain.'' rawahu Nasai ."
3554,"Hazrat abu-Ghalib se riwayat hai, abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ne raah dimashq par kuch sar nasab kiye huey dekhey to abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ( ye ( jahannam ke kuttey hain, aasman taley ye bad-tareen maqtool hain, aur unhoney jinhen qatl kya hai wo behtareen maqtool hain, phir unhoney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' us roz baaz chehrey safed hongey aur baaz chehrey siyah hongey .'' abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya, aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai? '' unhoney farmaya : agar maine usey ( bar-bar ( saat martaba tak na suna hota to main usey tumhen bayan na karta. Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
